<span id="fn_901"></span>[179:15](sbe1444.htm#fr_901.md) Colebrooke V, Dig.
CCCCXLIV; Vasish*th*a XVII, 86.

<span id="fn_902"></span>[180:18](sbe1444.htm#fr_902.md) Vasish*th*a IV,
23-25. Govinda points out that in case the second birth or death happens
